{
  "wireMagic": "pb3",
  "pens": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wsWinStyles": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wpWinPositions": [ {
  
  } ],
  "events": [ {
    "tStartMs": 150,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think there's also a\nlot of interesting things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1950,
    "dDurationMs": 3875,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to explore of multi-agent as\na form of test time compute."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 5825,
    "dDurationMs": 2275,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Basically letting Claude,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 8100,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "many Claudes work on a\nproblem can be, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 11340,
    "dDurationMs": 2200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "get you a better final\nanswer than just one."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 18450,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Hey, I'm Alex, I lead Claude\nRelations here at Anthropic."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21210,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Today we're gonna be talking about"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 22590,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "building more effective agents"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 24240,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I'm joined by my colleague."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 25680,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I'm Erik, I work on multi-agent research"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 27630,
    "dDurationMs": 900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "here at Anthropic."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 28530,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Erik, to kick us off here,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 30180,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "can you just explain why Claude\nis so good at agent tasks?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 33450,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, sure."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 34283,
    "dDurationMs": 1447,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So during our training,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 35730,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we let Claude practice being an agent."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 38250,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We give it open-ended\nproblems for it to work on"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 41190,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it can take many steps"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 43200,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and use tools, explore where\nit is and what it's working on"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 47520,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "before giving a final answer."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 49260,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And by getting lots of\npractice at being an agent,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 51780,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Claude becomes really good at this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 53280,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay, so it's these long running tasks"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 54870,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and a variety of domains basically."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 57330,
    "dDurationMs": 2688,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And through the process of RL"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 60018,
    "dDurationMs": 1212,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and other training mechanisms,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 61230,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Claude is learning an objective\nof how to do these things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 64710,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with basically limited\nguidance or feedback."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 67470,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Exactly, we do lots\nof RL on coding tasks,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 70620,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on search tasks, lots of things for Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 72990,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to practice being an agent\nin different environments."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 75090,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- There's kind of this conception,\nI think of Claude models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 77460,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that they're really,\nreally strong in code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 80130,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but that doesn't always maybe\ntransfer into other domains"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 82350,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or that coding is its own separate thing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 84360,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What are your kind of\nviews on that generally?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 86760,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- So coding has been the first task"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 88680,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we've really focused on,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 90270,
    "dDurationMs": 2233,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but once you have an amazing coding agent,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 92503,
    "dDurationMs": 2327,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a coding agent can do\nany other kind of work."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 94830,
    "dDurationMs": 3450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- If you need to do search,\nyou can do web search,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 98280,
    "dDurationMs": 4470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, via APIs, you\ncan plan a weekend by,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 102750,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, creating a schedule."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 104790,
    "dDurationMs": 3450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we really see coding as\na very fundamental skill"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 108240,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for an agent that's gonna have\na lot of spillover effect,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 110880,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be able to make Claude\ngreat at all sorts of things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 113490,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and sort of like train on\nthe hardest thing first"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 116040,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then everything else will become easy."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 117630,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- One interesting thing\nI've seen here recently"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 120120,
    "dDurationMs": 4770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with a feature that we released\nin Claude AI on the web"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 124890,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "was the ability for Claude\nto create actual files"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 128250,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "through writing code."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 129750,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So it was like writing a Python script"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 131970,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then the Python script got ran"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 133770,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and all of a sudden you\nhave like a Excel sheet"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 135960,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that popped out of that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 137160,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Is that kind of the future\ndirection that we're headed"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 138960,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is like Claude's writing scripts"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 140520,
    "dDurationMs": 3390,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and taking actions on\ncomputers to create files"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 143910,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or do things that are\ntraditionally not code related?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 146370,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think that's one of\nthe really effective ways"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 148410,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Claude will be able to do these things."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 150330,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Actually, just a few days\nago Claude was helping me"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 152430,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "make some diagrams for a presentation"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 154290,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it was able to create files"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 156000,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just by writing out the SVGs,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 158640,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but then I wanted it to make\na much more detailed diagram"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 161520,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that would need a lot of repetition"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 163620,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and so Claude was actually able to do this"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 165390,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "by writing some code to generate the SVG,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 168030,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which ran much, much\nfaster than Claude itself"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 170610,
    "dDurationMs": 930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "needing to write you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 171540,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it was a very, very repetitive image file"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 174960,
    "dDurationMs": 1990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with lots and lots of sort\nof detailed patterns in it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 176950,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah.\n- So, yeah,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 177783,
    "dDurationMs": 2487,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think that for a lot\nof cases writing code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 180270,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to produce some artifact\nwill be much better"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 183060,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "than just trying to create\nthat artifact directly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 185190,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So it's one way to do it for harder cases."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 187890,
    "dDurationMs": 870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay, right, yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 188760,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Code allows for kind of this speed up"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 191340,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that's not even possible with\nlike a human like clicking"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 193350,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and dragging and using\ntheir mouse on a computer."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 196260,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like repeated actions."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 197520,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Exactly, Claude gets a for loop."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 198990,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, if you're a developer"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 201000,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you're building an agent with Claude,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 203340,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "one thing that we've started\nto see become really popular"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 205170,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is this Claude Code SDK."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 206790,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Can you walk me through what that is"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 208170,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how you're seeing\ndevelopers starting to use that?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 210900,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so we're really\nexcited about developers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 212820,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "using the Claude Code SDK."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 214410,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This is something where\npreviously if you wanted"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 217470,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to build a coding agent\nor sort of any agent,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 220590,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you had to really go from"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 222990,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "nothing but hitting an API endpoint,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 225360,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "build the loops yourself,\nbuild all the tools,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 228180,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "build executing these tools,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 230190,
    "dDurationMs": 3330,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "interacting with files,\ninteracting with MCP."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 233520,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We basically have already built\nall of that into Claude Code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 236940,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and even though its name is Claude Code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 238590,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "really Claude Code is just\na general purpose agent"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 241290,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that is most often used for code."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 243030,
    "dDurationMs": 3450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Yeah, we are encouraging a lot\nof developers to use this SDK"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 246480,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as the core of their agent loop"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 248580,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that way they don't\nhave to spend a lot of time"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 251040,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "reinventing the wheel that\nwe've already put a lot of time"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 254400,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "into polishing and perfecting\nthat core agent loop"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 257190,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and instead they can use that"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 259050,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then just add their tools"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 261150,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for their own custom business logic"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 263460,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or affordances into that via MCP."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 265680,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right, so it offers that\nsort of customizability"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 268020,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to where you can remove\nthe coding-specific bits."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 270600,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Exactly.\n- And put in"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 271433,
    "dDurationMs": 2647,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "whatever sort of prompt\nor tools that you need,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 274080,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just like slots nicely into the scaffold."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 276120,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I think also the people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 277740,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "have been using Claude Code\nfor all sorts of things."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 279840,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think the, my strangest\nuse of Claude Code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 282450,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is I once had it plan a date for me"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 284400,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where I did a bunch of web searches,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 286200,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "found interesting activities\nand restaurants in the area"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 288480,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and so not code related at\nall, but it has all the tools."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 291660,
    "dDurationMs": 840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- How was the date?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 292500,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- It was pretty good."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 293760,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It was great, yeah.\n- Claude did a good job?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 295200,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, Filoli Gardens"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 296310,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then a Chinese restaurant nearby."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 297690,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Wow, okay.\n- Claude did a good job."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 299250,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I'm impressed.\n- Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 300083,
    "dDurationMs": 1777,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "One other thing on Claude Code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 301860,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that has been another popular feature"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 305040,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I've seen a lot of software\nengineers use lately"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 307200,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is Claude MD files."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 308940,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So these are files that you, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 311100,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "define within a project"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 312360,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and gives Claude relevant\ninformation about"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 314310,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what your programming style is"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 316110,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or like what the layout\nof the directories are,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 318510,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "things like that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 319343,
    "dDurationMs": 1717,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We've now launched a similar concept"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 321060,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that maybe takes a step\nfurther called Skills."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 323850,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Can you explain what Skills are"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 325200,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how we're starting to\nsee developers use them"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 327840,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and what they mean for Agents?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 329730,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so Claude Skills are\na very exciting extension"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 332610,
    "dDurationMs": 3660,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of Claude MD files where\ninstead of just giving it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 336270,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "notes files, you can\ngive it any sort of file."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 339060,
    "dDurationMs": 4530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That can be PowerPoint\ntemplate files, it can be code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 343590,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and like helper scripts\nthat you want it to use."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 346320,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It can be images or assets."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 349110,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think this extension\nof not just instructions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 351690,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but resources for the agent to use"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 354300,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is a really, really powerful\ntool where you might say,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 357450,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "not just these in are my instructions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 359310,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for making PowerPoint\npresentations, but here's, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 362280,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the head shots of all of\nour company leadership"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 364170,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you might need to\nreuse in many presentations"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 366540,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and just giving it all to\nClaude in a reusable way."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 368880,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So it has everything it needs right there."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 370380,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- One analogy I've heard used internally"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 373020,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I really, really like is,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 374700,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's kind of like in \"The Matrix\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 376140,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when Neo is learning kung\nfu for the first time"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 379500,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and they like inject him\nwith the Kung Fu information"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 382620,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and all of a sudden he\nis like a Kung Fu master."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 384510,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That feels like very similar\nto when I give Claude a skill"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 387240,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of some type of like, here's\nhow you create spreadsheets."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 389490,
    "dDurationMs": 1020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it's like, oh, all of a sudden"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 390510,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Claude's like a banker now"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 392070,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it can create a\nfinancial model for me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 394110,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- That and where they load in\nall of the racks of equipment"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 397050,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and tools and stuff for them to grab."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 398580,
    "dDurationMs": 902,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yes.\n- It's like, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 399482,
    "dDurationMs": 2398,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can start with these\nthings, not just instructions."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 401880,
    "dDurationMs": 840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I love that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 402720,
    "dDurationMs": 1050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Switching gears a little bit,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 403770,
    "dDurationMs": 4470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so last time we chatted on\ncamera here a few months back"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 408240,
    "dDurationMs": 1140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and we were talking about Agents"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 409380,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and at the time we were in this transition"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 411630,
    "dDurationMs": 3990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from maybe workflows which\nare like very defined ways"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 415620,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of how you chain together prompts"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 417780,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to what was just like\na single agent system"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 420480,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where you're running a model in a loop."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 422310,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Since then, what's been\nthe evolution in the space?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 425550,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so we've really seen\nAgents take over from workflows"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 428970,
    "dDurationMs": 3870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where Claude has gotten so\ngood at responding to feedback"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 432840,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and correcting its own work"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 434340,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that now Agent loops really\ndramatically outperform"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 438780,
    "dDurationMs": 3390,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "workflows for most things\nwhere you care most about"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 442170,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "absolute quality."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 443700,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Workflows are still great,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 444660,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where you need very low latency"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 445950,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you want Claude to just\ngive a best answer, single shot."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 448860,
    "dDurationMs": 2350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Agents are really, really\nhigh performance now."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 452160,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think one of the things that\nI've seen develop since then"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 455070,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is what I call workflows of Agents."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 458220,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Whereas previously an\napplication might have had"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 460440,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a workflow that had Claude in single shot"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 463260,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "write a SQL command in order to load data"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 465990,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then that would go to\nanother step in the workflow"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 468450,
    "dDurationMs": 4410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it would then write a\nchart to display that data."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 472860,
    "dDurationMs": 3690,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And if the SQL command\nfailed, you know this,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 476550,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it doesn't know that it's\nnot returning any data"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 478590,
    "dDurationMs": 1157,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then the second step of the workflow--"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 479747,
    "dDurationMs": 1303,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right.\n- Is kind of screwed."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 481050,
    "dDurationMs": 1080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Completely falls apart."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 482130,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- But now I've seen people\nwhere each one of those steps"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 484710,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the workflow is actually a closed loop"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 486990,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where instead of just\nwriting a single attempt"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 489570,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "at a SQL query, it then\nruns, Claude sees the output"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 493050,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then it can keep iterating and repeat"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 494730,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "until it knows that it got the right value"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 496920,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then it transitions to\nthe next step in the workflow."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 499470,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay, interesting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 500970,
    "dDurationMs": 3390,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So yes, this evolution I guess"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 504360,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of like chaining together prompts"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 506400,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to now chaining together\nagents in these loops themself,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 509100,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we'll see where that goes from there."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 511440,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "One other big topic of discussion,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 513750,
    "dDurationMs": 3130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I feel like that has taken a\nlot more chatter as of late"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 517920,
    "dDurationMs": 4530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is this question around\nobservability and verification."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 522450,
    "dDurationMs": 2439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Can you explain what that challenge is"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 524889,
    "dDurationMs": 1521,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how people are\nstarting to think about it?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 526410,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so observability\nis very hard for Agents,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 529350,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "especially as the systems get more complex"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 531540,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I think that's one of the reasons"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 533280,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where I still really believe"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 534600,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that even though the models\nare much more capable today"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 538080,
    "dDurationMs": 2925,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "than they were a year ago\nand they can work better"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 541005,
    "dDurationMs": 2355,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in an agent or even more complex setups,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 543360,
    "dDurationMs": 2850,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think that simplicity is\nstill a really important thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 546210,
    "dDurationMs": 4110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that even though you can\nbuild a big workflow of agents,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 550320,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you should still start sort of by"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 552450,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from the simplest possible thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 553770,
    "dDurationMs": 3570,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then work up to a\nmore complex solution."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 557340,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And you know, that's first\ntrying single shotting things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 559800,
    "dDurationMs": 4020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or trying, you know, single\nshot prompt to Claude Code SDK,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 563820,
    "dDurationMs": 3300,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is now just sort of such\na simple, easy thing to use."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 567120,
    "dDurationMs": 3030,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then I think only\nas needed adding layers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 570150,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and layers of complexity"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 571440,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because that's gonna make\nthe absorbability harder."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 573540,
    "dDurationMs": 3330,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Another term here maybe\nin parallel to workflows"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 576870,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of agents is multi-agent,\nis that the same thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 579420,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or is that something different?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 580920,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so multi-agent is my\nmain area of research now."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 584400,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'd say it's pretty different\nfrom a workflow of agent."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 586650,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay.\n- Workflows of agents,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 588540,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where sort of an one agent goes,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 590490,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "finishes and then it transitions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 592320,
    "dDurationMs": 3900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or its output gets sent to\nthe next agent to work on."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 596220,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Multi-agent is where fundamentally\nyou have multiple agents"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 599820,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or multiple Claudes\nworking at the same time"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 602520,
    "dDurationMs": 4620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where maybe one parent\nagent delegates tasks"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 607140,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to five sub-agents that can\neach then work in parallel."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 610320,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And this is how our deep research"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 612720,
    "dDurationMs": 3540,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "search product works is\nthe main orchestrator agent"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 616260,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "will decide and create several sub-agents."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 618870,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They can do lots of searches in parallel"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 620700,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that's way better for the user"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 622170,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because you know, all\nthis happens in parallel"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 624630,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you get the answer back much sooner."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 627330,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We also see things like in Claude Code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 630120,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the model will use a subagent."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 631590,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So if something, if some\nsub-task is gonna take"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 634740,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "tens of thousands of tokens,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 636000,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like maybe finding a certain\nimplementation of a class,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 639600,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but the answer really boils\ndown to something very small,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 642540,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it can do that work in a sub-agent"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 644790,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to protect the main\ncontext from all of that,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 648030,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "those tokens that aren't\nnecessary for the main work."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 650610,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So yeah, basically can\noffload this piece of work"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 653970,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and just get back the\nfinal answer that it needs."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 656130,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- So are we exposing then\nthis subagent in this case"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 659340,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is like a tool that Claude can call upon?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 662130,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Exactly.\n- Pass in,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 663450,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it'll pass in the prompt"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 664650,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as like a parameter or something?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 665940,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Exactly, yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 666773,
    "dDurationMs": 2737,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So to the, to Claude\nsub-agents look like a tool"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 669510,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it can pass\nprompts to the sub-agents"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 672420,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that will then go and do work."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 673800,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And part of my research is training Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 675870,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be a better manager and know how to--"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 677580,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Oh interesting.\n- Give clear instructions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 679020,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to its sub-agents and make sure"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 680250,
    "dDurationMs": 990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that they gets the right things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 681240,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and needs out of them."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 682073,
    "dDurationMs": 1297,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- How is this different than,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 683370,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or is this maybe like a specialized part"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 685410,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of tool calling overall or\nis it different in some ways?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 688020,
    "dDurationMs": 3870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I would say that this uses\nthe framework of tool calling"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 691890,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for that communication protocol"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 695040,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it just happens to\nbe a tool that itself"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 697050,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is backed by Claude, by another Claude."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 699000,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Does Claude have like\nan intuitive understanding"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 700950,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of what a subagent is or do\nwe have to like teach it?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 703920,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like you're actually\ntalking to another version"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 705960,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of yourself, Claude,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 707310,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like don't get freaked out sort of thing?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 709440,
    "dDurationMs": 3990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I would say that Claude makes\na lot of the same mistakes"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 713430,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that first time managers make"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 715110,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of where it will give incomplete"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 717810,
    "dDurationMs": 963,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or sort of unclear instructions."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 718773,
    "dDurationMs": 1887,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right, right.\n- To a sub-agent."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 720660,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right.\n- And you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 721493,
    "dDurationMs": 1657,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "kind of expect the subagent"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 723150,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to have the right context\nwhen actually it doesn't."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 725520,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think something we've seen"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 727410,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "during training on\nsub-agents is that Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 730140,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "starts to get much more\nverbose and much more detailed"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 732810,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and give its subagent the overall context"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 735150,
    "dDurationMs": 1070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of what's going on.\n- Interesting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 736220,
    "dDurationMs": 1690,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- So that they can do better work"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 737910,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that adds them to the whole, so."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 739200,
    "dDurationMs": 3990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'd say that, you know,\nit definitely Claude,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 743190,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Claude has a lot to learn"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 744300,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and is learning to get better at this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 745710,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay, cool.\n- Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 747000,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- What are, what are some\nof the use cases here?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 749070,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So their search is one in\nlike preserving context,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 752250,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is there other things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 753083,
    "dDurationMs": 2527,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that people are using\nmulti-agent for right now?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 755610,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I think coding is,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 757980,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there's a lot of subagent use in coding."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 760470,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Anything that can be\nparallelized or MapReduced."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 763200,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If you have something\nwhere you need to produce"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 765810,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a lot of output or there's maybe 10 parts"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 768930,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of some output you're creating,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 770340,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if you can split that\nup among 10 sub-agents,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 773490,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that can be really, really\neffective for saving context"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 776550,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and getting faster results."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 778440,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think there's also a lot of\ninteresting things to explore"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 780840,
    "dDurationMs": 3630,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of multi-agent as a form\nof test time compute."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 784470,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Basically letting Claude,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 786360,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "many Claudes work on a\nproblem can be, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 789630,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "get you a better final\nanswer than just one."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 791820,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Just like with people, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 792990,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a bunch of people putting\ntheir heads together"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 794520,
    "dDurationMs": 1080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "can get better results."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 795600,
    "dDurationMs": 3660,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- In that case, are we specializing\nthese agents in any way?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 799260,
    "dDurationMs": 3330,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Do we gear them towards like\none type of persona or another,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 802590,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or is it just kind of let\nthem take whatever form?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 805650,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think you can do either."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 807150,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, sometimes it's helpful\nto give a bunch of people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 809730,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the same exact task and see"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 811080,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what the different answers\nthey come up with are."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 813090,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Sometimes it's good to have many people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 814920,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or many agents work from\ndifferent approaches"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 816720,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to the same problem or split it up."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 819360,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "One thing I've seen a lot is customers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 822000,
    "dDurationMs": 3510,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that have a lot of tools,\nmaybe 100 or 200 tools"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 825510,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that they want an agent to use,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 827460,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they found that it's\nreally good to split up"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 829230,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "those tools among sub-agents."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 831090,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So the main agent, all\nit has to know is hey,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 833760,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I want to use this bucket of tools"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 836100,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then there's a subagent that goes"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 837720,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and does the actual work there."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 839340,
    "dDurationMs": 2850,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So that each subagent\njust has maybe 20 tools"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 842190,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that it needs to understand\nand know how to use."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 844320,
    "dDurationMs": 3540,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Have we tried like scaling\nagents like all the way up?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 847860,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like what happens if you\nhave like a thousand versions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 849720,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of Claude all working on one problem?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 851220,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Does it just turn into chaos?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 853290,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I've not tried that yet.\n- Okay."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 854730,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- But I'll get back to you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 855840,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Good research idea right there."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 857250,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What are some of other like failure modes"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 859350,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we're seeing right now\nwith agents or multi-agents?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 862770,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I think just like\nany sort of complex system,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 866490,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think it's easy to overbuild something"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 868440,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and lose a lot of efficiency"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 869850,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and just create sort of a\nlot of like dead weight."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 872490,
    "dDurationMs": 3390,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so I've seen overbuilt\nmulti-agent systems"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 875880,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "spend too much time just\ntalking back and forth"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 878280,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with each other and not\nactually making progress"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 880560,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on the main task, and you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 882300,
    "dDurationMs": 3690,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "human agents or human\norganizations suffer from the stew."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 885990,
    "dDurationMs": 1080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "As companies get bigger,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 887070,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you have more communication\noverhead and you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 889110,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "less and less work is actually, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 891000,
    "dDurationMs": 3450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the people on the ground\nmaking progress on things."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 894450,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- And so I think that's another\ninteresting thing to study"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 896310,
    "dDurationMs": 4530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is like how can we make\norganizations of Claudes"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 900840,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "very effective while\nkeeping the overhead small?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 903300,
    "dDurationMs": 3300,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- If I'm a developer and I want\nto get started with agents,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 906600,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "whether I'm building\non the Claude Code SDK"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 908400,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or just trying to on my\nown, do you have any tips"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 910740,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or best practices that you'd give them?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 912390,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I think the best\npractices really remain"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 915090,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "start simple and make sure, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 917340,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you only add complexities you need."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 919170,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think another really important thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 921090,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is think from the point\nof view of your agents."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 924060,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If you are giving Claude tools or prompts"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 927900,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or sort of any affordances,\nput yourself in Claude's shoes"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 931620,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and read what it actually\ngets, what it sees as the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 935460,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and make sure there's actually\nenough information there"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 937770,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for you to solve the problem."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 939720,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's very easy to sort\nof forget, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 942090,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we're seeing everything"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 943710,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the model only sees what we showed."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 946080,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right.\n- And it's."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 947040,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah.\n- Yeah, I feel like"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 948210,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's always important to go back"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 949620,
    "dDurationMs": 3990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "into like the raw transcript\nof like your tool calls"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 953610,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and your logs and everything\nand just view that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 956070,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Exactly, and I think another thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 957720,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that as people are\nbuilding more things like MCPS"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 960840,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and trying to connect\nClaude to more things,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 963060,
    "dDurationMs": 4650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think a very natural first\ninstinct that people have"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 967710,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that's very wrong is that an MCP"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 970530,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or tools should be\none-to-one with your API"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 973410,
    "dDurationMs": 3810,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I think actually tools\nfor the model or MCPs"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 977220,
    "dDurationMs": 4350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "should be one-to-one with\nyour UI, not your API."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 981570,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Because ultimately the model\nis a user of these things."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 984210,
    "dDurationMs": 3330,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's not, it doesn't work\nlike a traditional program."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 987540,
    "dDurationMs": 3450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So if your API might have\nthree separate endpoints"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 990990,
    "dDurationMs": 3570,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for say loading a Slack conversation"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 994560,
    "dDurationMs": 3330,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and turning a user ID into a username"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 997890,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and turning a channel\nID into a channel name."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1000020,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If those are the tools you give the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1001940,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to understand Slack, for\nit to understand anything,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1005300,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's gonna have to make three tool calls."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1007190,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Versus as a user, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1008600,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we just see everything\nall nicely rendered."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1010820,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Oh, that's interesting.\n- So you wanna create a tool"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1013010,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or an MCP for the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1014600,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that it presents everything all at once"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1017510,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with as little interaction as possible."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1019610,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Just like for a user it'll be terrible"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1021350,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if every time you had Slack"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1022460,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you had to like click on a user ID"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1024290,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to see what the name was, et cetera."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1026090,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right, right, I like that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1027350,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So kind of working back from\nlike the end state almost"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1030260,
    "dDurationMs": 1140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "instead of like just trying to map"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1031400,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the technical specs one to one."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1032960,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Exactly, and sort of surround"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1034460,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "whatever context you need with it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1035780,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- What do you think the future of Agents"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1038270,
    "dDurationMs": 930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "has in store for us?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1039200,
    "dDurationMs": 2850,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Any predictions on these\nnext six to 12 months?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1042050,
    "dDurationMs": 3090,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think Agents are gonna\nbecome a lot more pervasive"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1045140,
    "dDurationMs": 2850,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "sort of starting in\nareas that are verifiable"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1047990,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like software engineering."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1049850,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, coding agents have\nalready changed how I work"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1052100,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how tons of people at Anthropic work"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1055250,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I think there's still a huge amount"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1056870,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be be gained there."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1058040,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think one of the really\nexciting things is if agents"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1060980,
    "dDurationMs": 3090,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "can start getting better\nat verifying their own work"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1064070,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with things like computer use\nof, they can write a web app,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1067130,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but can they go actually\nopen it up and test it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1069680,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then find their own bug"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1071030,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "instead of you needing to do that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1072470,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think that's one of\nthe most exciting things."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1073640,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah.\n- Is like closing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1074900,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that loop of testing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1076130,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so that I don't have to\nbe Claude's QA engineer."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1078410,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right, so kind of\ncombining all these things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1080840,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from the software engineering abilities"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1082220,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to the computer use abilities"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1084230,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "once we put all these pieces together."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1086300,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yep, and I think the computer use"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1088310,
    "dDurationMs": 4230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is also gonna really open\nup a lot of other avenues"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1092540,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and domains where agents"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1093920,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "have been sort of locked out of so far."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1095690,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- What would be an example of that?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1097100,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think that if you want to have Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1098840,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "sort of do work for you in a Google Doc."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1101150,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah.\n- Right now it's,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1102260,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, Claude can write for you"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1103430,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but you're copy and\npasting back and forth."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1105290,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right.\n- But if you have computer use"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1106610,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you say, Hey Claude, can\nyou clean up this Google doc?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1109010,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It can just do it right there for you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1110270,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Scrolling around,\nclicking, editing the text"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1112730,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that's just such a nicer experience"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1114950,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "than needing to copy and\npaste back and forth."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1117080,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah.\n- It's like wherever you are,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1118490,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Claude can be there with you\nif it has with computer use."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1121130,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Well I'm very excited to have\nClaude write my Google Docs"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1123860,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and respond to all of my comments for me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1125510,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Exactly.\n- That'd be"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1126710,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a very nice future."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1128000,
    "dDurationMs": 1050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Erik, this has been great."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1129050,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Thank you so much for the conversation."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1130580,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Absolutely, thank you."
    } ]
  } ]
}
